<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Color and Border Fun</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #17a2b8;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .section-title {
      color: #17a2b8;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .box {
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #343a40;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <h1>Color and Border Fun</h1>
    <p>Learning how to add colors and borders with Bootstrap</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">My Favourite Activities</h2>

    <div class="box bg-warning border border-dark">
      <h3>Painting</h3>
      <p>I enjoy painting flowers, mountains, and bright sunsets.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box bg-success text-white border border-light">
      <h3>Gardening</h3>
      <p>I like watering plants and watching them grow.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box bg-primary text-white border border-dark">
      <h3>Swimming</h3>
      <p>I love swimming in clean water on a sunny day.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box bg-danger text-white border border-white">
      <h3>Sports</h3>
      <p>I play cricket and other outdoor games with my friends.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="section-title">Border Examples</h2>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="box bg-light border border-primary">
          Blue Border
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="box bg-light border border-success">
          Green Border
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="box bg-light border border-danger">
          Red Border
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid footer">
    <p>Made with Bootstrap — Color and Border Practice</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
